td.div: العربية: هذا العلم في عهد الحماية البريطانية رفعت في سفن فلسطين من عام 1927 حتى عام 1948 ميلادية.

English: The Palestine Ensign, flown by ships registered in the British Mandate territory during the period 1927–1948. This was the only Palestine-specific flag which was not restricted to official use by a government functionary or department (see Flag of the British Mandate for Palestine).

tr.td: Design data from FOTW and the existing WP image (PNG by AnonMoos, now deleted). Created from scratch using PD resources.
